    "# Sigma0 Stability Analysis\n",
    "Mirrors the sigma1/sigma2 stability notebooks but for **sigma0** (ISI=0).\n",
    "\n",
    "| Section | Question |\n",
    "|---------|----------|\n",
    "| A | Per-experiment-count stability at ISI=0 |\n",
    "| B | k_stimuli sensitivity |"
   ]
